headline: Progressive's 12th Annual Keys to Progress® Program Donates Nearly 100 Vehicles to Military Families
summary: As part of its ongoing commitment to drive progress on the road by providing reliable transportation for veterans, military-related organizations and veteran-owned small business owners across the country, Progressive Insurance® has announced its 12th annual Keys to Progress® vehicle giveaway event will take place Nov. 14, 2024.
